1. The Core Bridge

At the center of the web is this transformation:

Discrete integers → continuous waves

The mathematical engine doing this is the exponential rotation.

e^{ix}=\cos(x)+i\sin(x)

Interpretation:
	•	integers → countable steps
	•	exponentials → continuous change
	•	sine/cosine → geometry of circles

So one formula converts arithmetic → geometry → oscillation.

This is the first bridge.

